posting_body: ['4800 Excelsior', 'Leasing Office:', '4800 Excelsior Blvd', 'Saint Louis Park, MN 55416', 'show contact info', 'Take a look at what 4800 Excelsior has to offer!', "If you're looking for a luxurious apartment in Saint Louis Park, MN that offers the perfect blend of sophistication and relaxation, welcome to 4800Excelsior Apartment Homes.", "You'll feel like you're on permanent vacation with our charming West End location and winning combination of upscale living and resort-style conveniences, with shops, restaurants, and entertainment options just minutes away.", 'Rental Information:', '2 Bedroom / 2 Bathroom / 1067 sq ft / $2530 - $2575/Month', 'Lease Terms:', '3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month', 'Apartment Amenities:', '❖ Air Conditioning', '❖ Dining Room', '❖ Dishwasher', '❖ Energy Star Certified Appliances', '❖ Linen Closet', '❖ Microwave', '❖ Pantry', '❖ Walk-In Closets', '❖ Washer/Dryer', '❖ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms)', 'Additional Information:', '❖ 2 Elevators', '❖ Bike Storage', '❖ Coffee Station', '❖ Conference Room', '❖ Fireplace Lounge', '❖ Recycling', '❖ Resident Lounge', '❖ Rooftop Courtyard', '❖ Rooftop Terrace', '❖ Smoke Free', '❖ 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', '❖ 24-Hour Fitness Center', '❖ Barbecue/Grill Area', '❖ Controlled Access Building', '❖ Directly Above Fresh Thyme Farmers Market', '❖ On-site Maintenance & Management', '❖ Reservable Clubhouse', '❖ Rooftop Pool & Spa', '❖ Stretching/Yoga Room', '❖ Underground Heated Parking', 'Leasing Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Up to one month free!', 'Contact the leasing office for more information', 'Pet Policy:', 'Cats and Dogs Allowed: 75 lb Weight Limit.', '2 Pet Limit.', '$300 Refundable Deposit, $300 Non-Refundable Fee, $30/month/pet.', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Management Company:', 'Weidner Apartment Homes, LLC', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '26E42663E95F4E']
